  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safety and human dignity for migrants</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Crossing Mexico, migrants from Central America encounter one of the world&apos;s most dangerous migrant routes. Facing all kinds of violence, including torture and illegal detentions. Increased security and militarization augmented the danger. The Mexico&apos;s Southern Border Plan resulted in increased deportations, sending people back to the violence in their countries. We pressure the Mexican government to stop human rights violations of the migrants and guarantee their safety.</narrative>
  </description>
